{"id":"godhead","term":"Godhead","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>(<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Acts 17:29\">Acts 17:29</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Romans 1:20\">Rom. 1:20</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Colossians 2:9\">Col. 2:9</a>), the essential being or the nature of God.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Acts 17:29","Romans 1:20","Colossians 2:9"]}